42int err_load_crypto_strings_int(void)
43{
44 if (
45#ifndef OPENSSL_NO_ERR
46 ERR_load_ERR_strings() == 0 || /* include error strings for SYSerr */
47 ERR_load_BN_strings() == 0 ||
48# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_RSA
49 ERR_load_RSA_strings() == 0 ||
50# endif
51# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_DH
52 ERR_load_DH_strings() == 0 ||
53# endif
54 ERR_load_EVP_strings() == 0 ||
55 ERR_load_BUF_strings() == 0 ||
56 ERR_load_OBJ_strings() == 0 ||
57 ERR_load_PEM_strings() == 0 ||
58# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_DSA
59 ERR_load_DSA_strings() == 0 ||
60# endif
61 ERR_load_X509_strings() == 0 ||
62 ERR_load_ASN1_strings() == 0 ||
63 ERR_load_CONF_strings() == 0 ||
64 ERR_load_CRYPTO_strings() == 0 ||
65# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_COMP
66 ERR_load_COMP_strings() == 0 ||
67# endif
68# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_EC
69 ERR_load_EC_strings() == 0 ||
70# endif
71 /* skip ERR_load_SSL_strings() because it is not in this library */
72 ERR_load_BIO_strings() == 0 ||
73 ERR_load_PKCS7_strings() == 0 ||
74 ERR_load_X509V3_strings() == 0 ||
75 ERR_load_PKCS12_strings() == 0 ||
76 ERR_load_RAND_strings() == 0 ||
77 ERR_load_DSO_strings() == 0 ||
78# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_TS
79 ERR_load_TS_strings() == 0 ||
80# endif
81# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_ENGINE
82 ERR_load_ENGINE_strings() == 0 ||
83# endif
84# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_OCSP
85 ERR_load_OCSP_strings() == 0 ||
86# endif
87 ERR_load_UI_strings() == 0 ||
88# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_CMS
89 ERR_load_CMS_strings() == 0 ||
90# endif
91# ifndef OPENSSL_NO_CT
92 ERR_load_CT_strings() == 0 ||
93# endif
94 ERR_load_ASYNC_strings() == 0 ||
95#endif
96 ERR_load_KDF_strings() == 0 ||
97 ERR_load_OSSL_STORE_strings() == 0)
98 return 0;
99
100 return 1;
101}
